OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMichael Ball 'nervous' to  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsucceed DJ Steve Wright    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Michael Ball has admitted he is        
OL,6, "nervous" about taking over the late   
OL,7, Steve Wright's BBC Radio 2 Love Songs  
OL,8, show.                                  
OL,10,FThe Sunday request slot was hosted by  
OL,11,FWright from 1996 until the week before 
OL,12,Fhis death in February, aged 69.        
OL,14,FSinger Ball, who is English by birth   
OL,15,Fand with family hailing from south     
OL,16,FWales who inspired him to sing, will   
OL,17,Ftake over the programme in June.       
OL,19,F"I hope (Steve) will be pleased," said 
OL,20,Fthe 61-year-old.                       
